SELECT MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
 FROM sampled_keyword_4 AS k,
 sampled_movie_info_4 AS mi,
 sampled_movie_keyword_4 AS mk,
 sampled_title_4 AS t
 WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
 AND t.id = mk.movie_id
 AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
 AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
 AND k.keyword LIKE '@param0'
 AND mi.info IN ('@param1')
 AND t.production_year > @param2;

On the night of 14 November 1959, in Holcomb, Kansas, a farmhouse is broken into by the criminals Perry Smith and Dick Hickock that expect to get US$ 10,000.00.
